item.description:
Constitutional Scholar Diane Gilbert will be joining us to speak on our Constitution.

With all of the election activity I thought it proper for us to discuss the upcoming primary as well as what happens when our economy worsens. We will open up for discussion on the current issues such as Occupy Wall Street and the growing attacks they are levying on anyone they perceive to be not in their "99%".

We will discuss common sense preperations for you and your families.
item.name: Are you Prepared and guest speaker Diane Gilbert
